The paper deals with the integration and processing of heterogeneous data from multiple sources, which is a core problem in database systems (cs.DB). The use of an ontology to govern the integration process is a common approach in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses query rewriting and adaptation algorithms, which are relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR) and software engineering (cs.SE).
